metadata.name: Whispers of Petals
metadata.description:
An ode to the interconnectedness of worlds.

Through the delicate fusion of original photography and intricate vector art, this mixed-media piece unveils a tapestry that transcends boundaries and invites you to explore the unseen threads that connect all living things.

 Like whispers carried on a gentle breeze, the petals whisper their secrets, revealing the profound unity and harmony that permeates the vast tapestry of existence.


Mixed-media
5400 x 7200 px
